# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# POPY — Bangladesh Property Intelligence Platform
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values
# Free tier setup guide below each variable
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── DATABASE (PostgreSQL) ─────────────────────────────────────
# FREE: Render.com → New PostgreSQL → Free tier (90 days)
# OR: Neon.tech → Free tier (always free, 0.5GB)
# Format: postgresql://USER:PASS@HOST:PORT/DB_NAME
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://popy_user:yourpassword@dpg-xxx.render.com:5432/popy_db"

# ── AUTHENTICATION ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generate: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(64).toString('hex'))"
JWT_SECRET="your-super-secret-jwt-key-minimum-32-chars-change-this"

# App URL (update after Vercel deploy)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL="http://localhost:3000"

# ── AI / LLM (Property extraction + scoring) ─────────────────
# OpenAI: platform.openai.com → API keys → Free $5 credit
OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-..."

# OR Google Gemini: Free tier available
# GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY="AIzaSy..."

# ── EMAIL NOTIFICATIONS ───────────────────────────────────────
# Gmail: Enable 2FA → App Passwords → generate password
SMTP_HOST="smtp.gmail.com"
SMTP_PORT="587"
SMTP_USER="yourapp@gmail.com"
SMTP_PASS="your-gmail-app-password"
SMTP_FROM="POPY Platform <yourapp@gmail.com>"

# ── REDIS (Alert queue) ───────────────────────────────────────
# FREE: Upstash.com → Redis → Free tier (10,000 req/day)
REDIS_URL="redis://default:password@hostname.upstash.io:6379"

# ── FILE STORAGE (Raw HTML cache) ─────────────────────────────
# FREE: Cloudflare R2 → 10GB free/month
R2_ACCOUNT_ID=""
R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID=""
R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=""
R2_BUCKET_NAME="popy-raw-data"
R2_ENDPOINT="https://ACCOUNT_ID.r2.cloudflarestorage.com"

# ── PROXY (Optional — for scraping) ──────────────────────────
# BrightData / SmartProxy for anti-block rotation
# Leave empty to use direct connection (may get blocked)
PROXY_URL=""
PROXY_USERNAME=""
PROXY_PASSWORD=""

# ── GOOGLE SHEETS EXPORT ──────────────────────────────────────
# Google Apps Script webhook URL for auto-export
GOOGLE_SHEETS_WEBHOOK=""
